        <tags>cvss_base_vector=CVSS:3.0/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H|summary=PHP is prone to a denial of service (DoS) vulnerability.|insight=PHP mishandles property modification during __wakeup
