        <tags>cvss_base_vector=CVSS:3.0/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H|summary=Samba is prone to a denial of service (DoS) vulnerability.|insight=The flaw exists due to error in smbd
