        <tags>cvss_base_vector=CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:H/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N|summary=Oracle MySQL Server is prone to a vulnerability in a third party library.|insight=wolfSSL (formerly CyaSSL) as used in MySQL does not properly handle
