  - CVE-2021-21704: SIGSEGV in firebird_handle_doer.

  - CVE-2021-21704: SIGSEGV in firebird_stmt_execute.

  - CVE-2021-21704: Crash while parsing blob data in firebird_fetch_blob.|affected=PHP versions prior to 7.3.29.|impact=|solution=Update to version 7.3.29 or later.|vuldetect=Checks if a vulnerable version is present on the target host.|solution_type=VendorFix</tags>
