  execution when a ProxyCommand is used.|affected=OpenBSD OpenSSH versions prior to 10.1.|impact=|solution=Update to version 10.1 or later.|vuldetect=Checks if a vulnerable version is present on the target host.|solution_type=VendorFix</tags>
